{"tid":2059540,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"楊潤雄：所謂罷課公投是推動反對國安法　應該制止","createTime":"2020-06-11T04:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T04:56:36.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1b8a8bae75db4c061b32841b0b49ba45eb187072","tid":2059540,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T04:10:20.000Z","msg":"有團體發起「罷工罷課公投」，收集學生對反對「港區國安法」的意見及罷課意向。教育局局長楊潤雄重申，所謂公投背後是推動反對國家安全立法，這是不能接受，應該制止。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄說，專業老師不應罷課，學生也不應浪費時間做無謂的事。他又說，很難「逐首歌」評論是否不應在校園內唱，但反修例歌曲《願榮光歸香港》很明顯是政治宣傳歌曲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531421-20200611.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531421-20200611.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=5b80d9f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531421-20200611.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=bb0cbe2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531421-20200611.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"b0fd96f5ba04a47b57ab232132632444dcb3e090","tid":2059540,"uid":269608,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T04:11:46.000Z","msg":"反對國安法係犯左乜法？"},{"pid":"1562061955743f27c7183c0d7b1ba86d8e360c83","tid":2059540,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T04:11:47.000Z","msg":"《基本法》第27條：香港居民享有言論、新聞、出版的自由，結社、集會、遊行、示威的自由，組織和參加工會、罷工的權利和自由。<br />\n<br />\n《基本法》第39條：《公民及政治權利國際公約》97年後在港繼續有效。"},{"pid":"4e60953776dac9f6732ce939e5d00cd0f314e050","tid":2059540,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b0fd96f5ba04a47b57ab232132632444dcb3e090","tid":2059540,"uid":269608,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T04:11:46.000Z","msg":"反對國安法係犯左乜法？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T04:12:08.000Z","msg":"妄議朝政"},{"pid":"8d4fedc778a35cb563b70e3d61111d6a31242c8b","tid":2